### Active Directory API Test Requests

### Health Checks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/ad

### User Operations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/john.doe
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/email/john.doe@company.com
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/dn/CN=John Doe,OU=Users,DC=company,DC=com

### User Search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "searchTerm": "john",
  "maxResults": 50,
  "attributes": ["displayName", "email", "department"]
}

### User Authentication
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john.doe",
  "password": "password123"
}

### User Groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/john.doe/groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/john.doe/groups/Administrators/ismember

### Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": {
    "samAccountName": "jane.smith",
    "displayName": "Jane Smith",
    "givenName": "Jane",
    "surname": "Smith",
    "email": "jane.smith@company.com",
    "enabled": true
  },
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### Update User
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/jane.smith
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "samAccountName": "jane.smith",
  "displayName": "Jane Smith",
  "givenName": "Jane",
  "surname": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@company.com",
  "enabled": true,
  "department": "IT",
  "title": "Software Developer"
}

